			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It&#8217;s almost time for the last issue of A Man Called Edgar Snatch to be released. I plan to post the last installment of the current series within a few days, to wrap up the story of Edgar Snatch.</p>
<p>The final installment will answer a few questions, and pose a few more.</p>
<p><span id="more-894"></span></p>
<p>Since <em>Snatch and the Last Laugh </em>is ready and will be released soon, I wanted to invite everyone to go back and read the <a title="A Man Called Edgar Snatch" href="http://elijahtoten.com/series/a-man-called-edgar-snatch/">series from the start</a>.</p>
<p>Now that more details have become available, more of the story will make sense and details that seemed trivial before may now indeed play an integral part to the story. Go check it out, and stay tuned for the final installment in the next few days.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></content:encoded>
